  <h2>Technical Stack</h2>

  <ul>
    <li><b>Data Generation:</b> Python</li>
    <li><b>Database Development:</b> MySQL (DDL, Stored Procedures, Views)</li>
    <li><b>Business Intelligence:</b> Power BI</li>
    <li><b>Languages:</b> SQL, DAX, Python</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Key Takeaways</h2>

  <p>This project demonstrates the full pipeline from dataset creation to database development and business intelligence reporting for a realistic marketing use case. By combining automated SQL calculations and Power BI visualizations, we developed a scalable environment to analyze marketing KPIs and optimize business decisions.</p>

